title: Anastasia Beverly Hills Lash Genius Waterproof Topcoat 0.19 oz.
description: Anastasia Beverly Hills Lash Genius Waterproof Topcoat makes it easy to waterproof any mascara. Simply brush this lightweight formula over your mascara and it seals it from running and smudging. It glides on smoothly and refreshes mascara that's starting to flake, as well as leaves your lashes with a high-shine finish.

title: Konad Nail Art Double Ended Stamper And Scraper
description:
This stamper has 2 ends with different sizes and colours. Great when stamping small images or for childrens nails. The green stamper is ideal when using red special polish because the red image shows up better on the green stamper.
